Package: ParCC
Title: Parameter Converter and Calculator for HTA
Version: 1.3.0
Authors@R: person("RRC-HTA", "Team", email = "hta.aiimsbhopal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A decision support tool for Health Technology Assessment (HTA).
    Bridges the gap between clinical evidence and economic models by automating
    complex parameter estimations including rate-probability conversions,
    hazard ratio-based probability conversion, survival extrapolation,
    PSA distribution fitting, and value-based pricing analysis.
